name: Money Dogs
description: Money Dogs started as a Play-to-Earn (P2E) meme token on the TON blockchain and $MDOGS went through a hypergrowth becoming one of the fastest growth meme project in TON ecosystem. In order to become a sustainable platform, Money Dogs is evolving into a platform with Game Center and Launchpool to keep community engaged. The project is focused on showing the story of how a meme project can be quickly developed thanks to our community and how we are turning this to reward our community through upcoming success.
